com.kuka.device

Interface IControllerDevice


  • public interface IControllerDevice
    Via this capability, devices managed by a controller provide an identifying name and enable access to their controller's capabilities.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      com.kuka.capabilities.ICapabilityContainer getControllerCapabilities()
      Gets the capability container providing access to the capabilities of the device controller.
      String getControllerName()
      Gets the name of the controller this device is controlled by.
      String getName()
      Gets the name of the device.

    • Method Detail

      • getName

        String getName()
        Gets the name of the device. The returned name has the special property that it identifies the device on the controller. In many cases this might be the same as the display name, but it doesn't always need to be this way.
        Returns:
        the name of the device for identification purposes.

      • getControllerName

        String getControllerName()
        Gets the name of the controller this device is controlled by.
        Returns:
        the name of the controller.

      • getControllerCapabilities

        com.kuka.capabilities.ICapabilityContainer getControllerCapabilities()
        Gets the capability container providing access to the capabilities of the device controller.
        Returns:
        the capability container providing access to the capabilities of the device controller.
